		<div>Here's the latest rumor about who's in the upcoming live-action EVA movie.<br />
<br />
<a href="http://www.futurizmo.com/anime/news/EpVlkuukFEkgdZxXWT.php" target="_blank">Daniel Radcliffe As Shinji Ikari In Live Action EVA?<br />
</a></div>
