		<hr />
		
		
		
		
		<div>Radcliffe isn't whiny enough to be Shinji Ikari.  Shinji is an emotionally unstable teenager who is constantly looking for support and help from other people to live his life.  In those few lucid moments that he actually has some self esteem he really shines, but otherwise he's normally whiny and sullen.<br />
<br />
Of course I found Shinji's whining to be highly annoying at times.  Maybe Daniel Radcliffe and insert some more personality into the character that was lacking in the series. :)</div>
	</td>
</tr>
</table>
<br /><table class="tborder" cellpadding="6" cellspacing="1" border="0" width="100%">
<tr>
	<td class="page">
	
